item.title: CVE-2022-24661|2024-08-03T04:20:49.070Z -- siemens -- simcenter%20star-ccm%2B%20viewer
item.description: A vulnerability has been identified in Simcenter STAR-CCM+ Viewer (All versions < V2022.1). The starview+.exe contains a memory corruption vulnerability while parsing specially crafted .SCE files. This could allow an attacker to execute code in the context of the current process.
